{
  "meta": {
    "is_partial": true,
    "description": "주문 상세 - 배송지 정보"
  },
  "type": "basic",
  "name": "Div",
  "props": { "className": "bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6" },
  "responsive": {
    "portable": {
      "props": { "className": "bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4" }
    }
  },
  "children": [
    {
      "comment": "섹션 제목 + 배송지 수정 버튼",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": { "className": "flex items-center justify-between mb-4 pb-4 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700" },
      "responsive": {
        "portable": {
          "props": { "className": "flex items-center justify-between mb-3 pb-3 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700" }
        }
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-2" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Icon",
              "props": { "name": "truck", "size": "md",
              "className": "text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300" }
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "H3",
              "props": { "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
              "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.shipping_title",
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" }
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "배송지 수정 버튼 - 배송 전 상태 (회원/비회원 공통). 공유 partial 이라 비회원 상세(guest_order_show)에서도 재사용되며, 비회원은 모달에서 탭 없이 직접입력 폼만 노출된다.",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Button",
          "if": "{{order.data.order_status === 'pending_payment' || order.data.order_status === 'payment_complete'}}",
          "props": { "type": "button", "className": "inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors" },
          "children": [
            { "type": "basic", "name": "Icon", "size": "sm", "props": { "name": "pen-to-square" } },
            { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.change_shipping_address" }
          ],
          "actions": [
            {
              "comment": "배송지 변경 모달 열기 — 모달은 부모 _local 을 못 읽으므로(별도 컨텍스트), 공유 상태를 _global 로 전달. 열 때마다 전부 덮어써서 이전 잔존값 무해화. changeAddressMode 는 회원=saved(탭 선택 가능)/비회원=manual(탭 없이 직접입력) 분기. 직접입력 초기값은 현재 배송지(order.data.shipping_address). _modal_address.json(_global.editingAddress) 와 동일 패턴.",
              "type": "click",
              "handler": "sequence",
              "actions": [
                {
                  "handler": "setState",
                  "params": {
                    "target": "global",
                    "changeAddressMode": "{{_global.currentUser?.uuid ? 'saved' : 'manual'}}",
                    "selectedAddressId": null,
                    "editingShippingAddress": {
                      "recipient_name": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.recipient_name ?? ''}}",
                      "recipient_phone": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.recipient_phone ?? ''}}",
                      "zipcode": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.zipcode ?? ''}}",
                      "address": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.address ?? ''}}",
                      "address_detail": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.address_detail ?? ''}}",
                      "region": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.region ?? ''}}",
                      "city": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.city ?? ''}}"
                    }
                  }
                },
                { "handler": "openModal", "target": "changeAddressModal" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "배송지 정보 목록",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": { "className": "space-y-3" },
      "children": [
        {
          "comment": "받는 분",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-start" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "w-28 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" },
              "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.shipping_name",
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "w-20 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm" }
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
              "text": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.recipient_name ?? ''}}",
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm" }
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "배송국가 (D9 — 항상 표시, KR 포함)",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-start" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "w-28 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" },
              "text": "$t:shop.checkout.shipping_country",
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "w-20 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm" }
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
              "text": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.recipient_country_name?.[_global.locale] ?? order.data.shipping_address?.recipient_country_name?.ko ?? order.data.shipping_address?.recipient_country_code ?? 'KR'}}",
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm" }
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "연락처",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-start" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "w-28 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" },
              "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.shipping_phone",
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "w-20 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm" }
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
              "text": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.recipient_phone ?? ''}}",
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm" }
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "주소",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-start" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "w-28 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" },
              "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.shipping_address",
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "w-20 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm" }
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
              "text": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.full_address ?? ''}}",
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm" }
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "배송 메모 (있는 경우만 표시)",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.delivery_memo_label || order.data.shipping_address?.delivery_memo}}",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-start" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "w-28 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" },
              "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.shipping_memo",
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "w-20 flex-shrink-0 text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-sm" }
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
              "text": "{{order.data.shipping_address?.delivery_memo_label ?? order.data.shipping_address?.delivery_memo ?? ''}}",
              "responsive": {
                "portable": {
                  "props": { "className": "text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm" }
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "배송 현황 — 결제 완료 이후 OrderStatusEnum 값(payment_complete/shipping_hold/preparing/shipping_ready/shipping/delivered/confirmed)에서만 노출. pending_order/pending_payment 상태에서는 '배송대기' 라벨 노출이 사용자에게 모호하므로 비표시 (결제 안내가 우선). cancelled 도 비표시 — 취소된 주문은 배송 현황 무의미. (부분취소는 별도 상태가 아니라 잔여 옵션 기준 진행 상태로 환원되어 배송 현황이 정상 노출됨.)",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{(order.data.shippings ?? []).length > 0 && ['payment_complete','shipping_hold','preparing','shipping_ready','shipping','delivered','confirmed'].includes(order.data.order_status)}}",
      "props": { "className": "mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 space-y-3" },
      "responsive": {
        "portable": {
          "props": { "className": "mt-3 pt-3 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 space-y-2" }
        }
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-2 mb-2" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Icon",
              "props": { "name": "box", "size": "sm",
              "className": "text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300" }
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "props": { "className": "text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" },
              "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.shipping_status_title"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "배송 목록",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "space-y-3" },
          "iteration": { "source": "{{order.data.shippings ?? []}}", "item_var": "shipping" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Div",
              "props": { "className": "bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700/50 rounded-lg p-3 space-y-2" },
              "children": [
                {
                  "comment": "배송 상태 + 정책명",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "props": { "className": "flex items-center justify-between" },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Div",
                      "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-2" },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Span",
                          "props": { "className": "text-sm font-medium {{shipping.shipping_status_variant === 'success' ? 'text-green-600 dark:text-green-400' : shipping.shipping_status_variant === 'warning' ? 'text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-400' : shipping.shipping_status_variant === 'danger' ? 'text-red-600 dark:text-red-400' : 'text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400'}}" },
                          "text": "{{shipping.shipping_status_label ?? ''}}"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "basic",
                          "name": "Span",
                          "if": "{{shipping.delivery_policy_snapshot?.policy_name}}",
                          "props": { "className": "text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" },
                          "text": "({{shipping.delivery_policy_snapshot?.policy_name ?? ''}})"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "배송비 금액 — 0원이면 '무료' 라벨(녹색), 그 외 금액 포맷. Number() 캐스팅으로 decimal:2 문자열도 안전 비교 (_payment.json 와 동일 패턴).",
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "props": { "className": "text-sm font-medium {{Number(shipping.total_shipping_amount ?? 0) === 0 ? 'text-green-600 dark:text-green-400' : 'text-gray-900 dark:text-white'}}" },
                      "text": "{{Number(shipping.total_shipping_amount ?? 0) === 0 ? '$t:mypage.order_detail.free_shipping' : (shipping.mc_total_shipping_amount?.[_global.preferredCurrency ?? 'KRW']?.formatted ?? shipping.total_shipping_amount_formatted ?? '')}}"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "comment": "배송비 상세 (기본/추가/할인)",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "if": "{{(shipping.extra_shipping_amount ?? 0) > 0 || (shipping.shipping_discount_amount ?? 0) > 0}}",
                  "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-3 text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.base_shipping {{shipping.base_shipping_amount_formatted ?? ''}}"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{(shipping.extra_shipping_amount ?? 0) > 0}}",
                      "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.extra_shipping +{{shipping.extra_shipping_amount_formatted ?? ''}}"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{(shipping.shipping_discount_amount ?? 0) > 0}}",
                      "props": { "className": "text-red-400 dark:text-red-500" },
                      "text": "$t:mypage.order_detail.shipping_discount -{{shipping.shipping_discount_amount_formatted ?? ''}}"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "comment": "택배사/운송장 (있을 때)",
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Div",
                  "if": "{{shipping.carrier_name || shipping.tracking_number}}",
                  "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-2 text-sm" },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{shipping.carrier_name}}",
                      "props": { "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" },
                      "text": "{{shipping.carrier_name ?? ''}}"
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "운송장 번호 — tracking_url 있으면 택배사 배송조회 링크",
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "A",
                      "if": "{{shipping.tracking_url}}",
                      "props": {
                        "href": "{{shipping.tracking_url}}",
                        "target": "_blank",
                        "rel": "noopener noreferrer",
                        "className": "text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-medium underline hover:text-blue-800 dark:hover:text-blue-300"
                      },
                      "text": "{{shipping.tracking_number ?? ''}} ($t:mypage.order_detail.track_shipment)"
                    },
                    {
                      "comment": "운송장 번호 폴백 — tracking_url 없을 때 텍스트만",
                      "type": "basic",
                      "name": "Span",
                      "if": "{{!shipping.tracking_url && shipping.tracking_number}}",
                      "props": { "className": "text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-medium" },
                      "text": "{{shipping.tracking_number ?? ''}}"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
